Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:15.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi. I've got an appointment with Mr. Ullman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My name is Jack Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His office is the first door on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:39.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Mr. Ullman? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:43.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm Jack Torrance. - Oh, come on in, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:45.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice to meet you too, Mr. Ullman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- This is my secretary, Susie. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Susie, how do you do? - Any trouble finding us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:54.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No problem at all. I made the trip in 3 and a half hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's very good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sit down a minute, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you like some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you're having some, I wouldn't mind. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:06.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Susie. - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And would you ask Bill Watson to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:09.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:27.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you really want to go and live in that hotel for the winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:29.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It'll be lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:39.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyway, there's hardly anybody to play with around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:45.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know. It always takes a little time to make new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:52.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's looking forward to the hotel, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I ain't, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:58.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, come on, Tony. Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:00.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to go there, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How come you don't want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:11.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're all going to have a real good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bill, I'd like you to meet Jack Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How do you do, Bill? - How do you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Nice to meet you. - Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grab a chair, Bill. Join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack is going to take care of the Overlook for us this winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:28.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd like you to take him around place soon as we're through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack is a schoolteacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh, formerly a schoolteacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What line of work are you in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:42.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Teaching's been more or less a way of making ends meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This ought to be quite a change for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:47.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I'm looking for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:50.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our people in Denver recommended Jack very highly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:51.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I agree with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:54.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's see, where were we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:56.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was ,yeah, about to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:02.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that our season here runs from may 15th to October 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:06.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then we close down completely until the following May.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:08.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you mind if I ask why you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:13.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It seems to me that the skiing up here would be fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It would be. The problem is the enormous cost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it would be to keep the road to Sidewinder open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:20.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a 25-mile stretch of road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It gets 20 feet of snow during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:28.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's just no way to make it economically feasible to keep it clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When the place was built in 1907...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:34.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there was very little interest in winter sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:39.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This site was chosen for its seclusion and scenic beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's certainly got plenty of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did they give you any idea in Denver...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about what the job entails?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:51.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only in a very general way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The winters can be fantastically cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:00.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The basic idea is to cope with the very costly damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:02.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and depreciation which can occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This consists mainly of running the boiler...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:08.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}heating different parts of the hotel on a daily rotating basis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:11.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}repairing damage as it occurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:14.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and doing repairs so the elements can't get a foothold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That sounds fine to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Physically, it's not a very demanding job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The only thing that can
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}get a bit trying here during the winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:27.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is a tremendous sense of isolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:32.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that just happens to be exactly what I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:36.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm outlining a new writing project.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:40.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, five months of peace is just what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's very good, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:46.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because, for some people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}solitude ...and isolation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:53.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}can, of itself, become a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How about your wife and son?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you think they'll take to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:04.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:09.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, before I turn you over to Bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:14.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there's one other thing I think we should talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to sound melodramatic,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it's something been known to give a few people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}second thoughts about the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't suppose they tell you anything in Denver
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:29.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about the tragedy we had up here during the winter of 1970.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't believe they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My predecessor in this job
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}hired a man named Charles Grady as the winter caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:43.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He came up with his wife and two little girls
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of about 8 and 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He had a good employment record,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:47.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}good references.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And from what I've been told,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he seemed like a completely normal individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But at some point during the winter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:56.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he must have suffered
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}some kind of a complete mental breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He ran amuck and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:07.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}killed his family with an ax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:13.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stacked them neatly in a room in the west wing, and then he...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:17.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he put both barrels of his shotgun in his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The police...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:25.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they thought that it was what the old-timers used to call cabin fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A kind of claustrophobic reaction which can occur
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:32.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when people are shut in together over long periods of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:38.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}quite a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:43.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's still hard for me to believe it actually happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:55.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think you can appreciate why I wanted to tell you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I certainly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:02.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I also understand why your people in Denver
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}left it for you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:08.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Obviously, some people can be put off
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:10.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}by the idea of staying alone in a place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where something like that actually happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, you can rest assured Mr. Ullman,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that's not going to happen with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:21.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And as far as my wife is concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:25.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure she'll be absolutely fascinated when I tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:31.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's a confirmed ghost story and horror film addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony, do you think dad'll get the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:47.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's going to phone Wendy up in a few minutes to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:02.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:05.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hi, babe. - Hi, hon. How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:07.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great. Look, I'm at the hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I still have a awful lot to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:12.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think I can get home before 9:00 or 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:14.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sounds like you got the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:17.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right. It's a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You and Danny are going to love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony, why don't you want to go to the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:25.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You do too know. Now come on, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, Tony, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, hold your eyes still so I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's good. Now the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, Danny
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when you were brushing your teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:36.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}do you remember if you smelled anything funny
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:39.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or saw any bright, flashing lights
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:41.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or anything at all strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:45.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you remember when you were brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:55.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the next thing you remember after you were brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:03.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My mom was saying, "Wake up. Wake up, Danny, wake up. "
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:08.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, Danny, can you remember what you were doing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just before you started brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Talking to Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is Tony one of your animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. He's a little boy that lives in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:25.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony's his imaginary friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:31.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you were to open your mouth now, could I see Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:33.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because he hides.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:40.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where does he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:49.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does Tony ever tell you to do things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:55.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to talk about Tony anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:57.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:06.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm going to ask you to do me a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:10.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and stay quietly in bed for the rest of the day. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes. I'd like you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're going in the other room for a few minutes and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll come back and check on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:19.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Okay?  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:20.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Shall we go into the living room? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Please. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:43.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mrs. Torrance, I don't think you have anything to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:47.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm quite sure there's nothing physically wrong with Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:49.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:55.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He seems absolutely fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you should've seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kids can scare you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:03.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But believe me, these episodes are not at all uncommon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And they look much worse than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But what was the matter with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mrs. Torrance, Most of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:13.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}these episodes with kids are never explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:19.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're brought on by emotional factors and rarely occur again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:22.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're more akin to autohypnosis
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A kind of self-induced trance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:28.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If it reoccurs, which I doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we can always think about having some tests done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:33.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you been in Boulder long, Mrs. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only about three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:46.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're from Vermont. My husband was teaching school there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:52.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did the appearance of Danny's imaginary friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did Tony's first appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}happen to coincide with your arrival here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess Danny started talking to Tony
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:08.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about the time we put him in nursery school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did he adjust well to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:13.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't like it too much at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:19.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then he had an injury, so we kept him out for a while and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I guess that's about
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:24.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when I first noticed he was talking to Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What sort of injury did he have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He dislocated his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How did he manage to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:40.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was just one of those things, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:41.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Purely an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:46.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My husband had been drinking and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:48.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he came home about three hours late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:54.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So he wasn't exactly in the greatest mood that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:59.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Danny had scattered some of his school papers all over the room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:03.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and my husband grabbed his arm to pull him away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just the sort of thing you do 100 times with a child
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know, in a park or in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But on this particular occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:16.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my husband just used too much strength
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:19.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he injured Danny's arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:25.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anyway, something good did come out of it all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:26.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because he said:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Wendy, I'm never going to touch another drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if I do, you can leave me. "
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:37.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He hasn't had any alcohol in 5 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:42.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:04.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:09.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We must really be high up. The air feels so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:15.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:19.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You should've eaten your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:28.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll get you something as soon as we get to the hotel. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wasn't it around here that the Donner party got snowbound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:41.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think that was farther west, in the Sierras.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:44.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What was the Donner party?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:51.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They were a party of settlers in covered wagon times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They got snowbound one winter in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:59.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They had to resort to cannibalism in order to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You mean they ate each other up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:06.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They had to in order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't worry, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:13.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know all about cannibalism. I saw it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:16.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He saw it on the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What time does the plane leave? - 8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:55.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That gives us plenty of time to go over everything first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Goodbye, Mr. Ullman. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:20:00.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning, Jack. I hope you haven't been waiting too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:03.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No problem. In fact we had time to grab a bite to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good. Glad you made it before they shut down the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hi. - Is your family having a look around?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:11.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, my son's discovered the games room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Has your luggage been brought in? - Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In view of all the ground we have to cover today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:20.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I suggest we have a quick look at your apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and get started straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:23.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bill, would you have the Torrances' things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:24.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}brought to their apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Fine. - I'd better collect my family first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:38.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is our Colorado Lounge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:42.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This place is fantastic, isn't it, hon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:49.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've never seen anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are all these Indian designs authentic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:59.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe they're based mainly on Navajo and Apache motifs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're really gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:01.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As a matter of fact
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:05.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this is probably the most gorgeous hotel I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:08.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This old place has had an illustrious past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:12.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In its heyday, it was one of the stopping place for the jet setters
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:15.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}even before anybody knew what a jet set was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:18.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We had four presidents who stayed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lots of movie stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:21.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:23.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All the best people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:19.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the staff wing of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:23.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}None of the other bedrooms are heated during the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:26.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Goodbye, Mr. Ullman. - Goodbye, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:29.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And here are your quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:32.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Living room, bedroom, bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.42,0:22:34.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And a small bedroom for your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.53,0:22:40.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perfect for a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:41.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:51.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, then. Place is very nicely self-contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:52.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Easy to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:56.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:58.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, very cozy for a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.52,0:23:01.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you feel like spreading out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:03.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you have the rest of the hotel to move around in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.73,0:23:07.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it's very...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.73,0:23:09.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}homey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:11.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:15.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is our famous hedge maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:19.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's quite an attraction here. The walls are 13 feet high
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:22.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the hedge is as old as the hotel itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:23.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A lot of fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I wouldn't want to go in there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}unless I had an hour to spare to find my way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:31.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When was the Overlook built?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:35.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Construction started in 1907.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:36.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was finished in 1909.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:40.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The site's supposed to be on an Indian burial ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:42.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I believe they actually had to repel
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.11,0:23:44.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a few Indian attacks as they were building it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.53,0:23:47.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's our Snowcat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:49.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you both drive a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:50.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.68,0:23:51.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:54.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because basically the Snowcat operates very much like a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:56.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It won't take you long to get the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:23:58.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As a matter of fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.42,0:24:02.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we brought a decorator in from Chicago just last year
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:04.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to refurbish this part of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.18,0:24:07.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He sure did a beautiful job.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:09.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pink and gold are my favorite colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:12.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, this is our Gold Ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.50,0:24:15.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll say!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:19.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can accommodate up to 300 people here very comfortably.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:23.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boy, I bet you we could really have a good party in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:25.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm afraid you won't do too well here
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:27.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}unless you brought supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:30.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We always remove the booze from the premises when we shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.56,0:24:33.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That reduces the insurance we normally have to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.81,0:24:35.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.36,0:24:36.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then you're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:41.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dick, come on over and say hello to Mr. and Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.06,0:24:43.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Dick Hallorann, our head chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.29,0:24:45.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Mr. Hallorann, I'm Jack. - Glad to meet you, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.39,0:24:46.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is my wife, Winifred.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.33,0:24:47.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Glad to meet you, Winifred. - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.61,0:24:50.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Torrances are gonna take care of the Overlook for us this winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.18,0:24:55.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's just great. How do you folks like our hotel so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.02,0:24:56.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.79,0:24:57.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, Danny!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.16,0:25:01.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I found him outside looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:05.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dan, did you get tired of bombing the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.85,0:25:06.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.36,0:25:08.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.61,0:25:10.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Thanks. - Thank you, Susie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.45,0:25:12.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dick, if you're ready to do it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.04,0:25:14.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think it'd be a good idea if you could show Mrs. Torrance the kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.85,0:25:16.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}while I continue on with Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:19.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It would be a pleasure. Right this way, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.36,0:25:21.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great. See you later, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.13,0:25:22.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bye, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.19,0:25:26.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.86,0:25:28.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mrs. Torrance, your husband introduced you as Winifred.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.48,0:25:30.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, are you a "Winnie," or a "Freddie"?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.13,0:25:32.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm a Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.64,0:25:35.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Wendy. That's nice. That's the prettiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.00,0:25:37.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God, this is the kitchen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.81,0:25:39.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.57,0:25:42.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do you like it, Danny? Is it big enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.17,0:25:45.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. It's the biggest place I ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.88,0:25:48.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, this whole place is such an enormous maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.39,0:25:49.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I feel like I'll have to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.30,0:25:51.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}leave a trail of breadcrumbs every time I come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.81,0:25:54.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't let it get you down, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.94,0:25:57.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's big, but it still ain't nothing but a kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.61,0:25:59.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And a lot of this stuff you'll never have to touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.90,0:26:02.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wouldn't know what to do with it if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.40,0:26:05.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, one thing for sure, you don't have to worry about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.73,0:26:08.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because ou folks could eat up here a whole year
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.75,0:26:10.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and never have the same menu twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.61,0:26:14.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, right here is our walk-in freezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.11,0:26:17.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, this is where we keep all of our meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.18,0:26:20.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got 15 rib roasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.40,0:26:22.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}30 ten-pound bags of hamburger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.73,0:26:26.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got 12 turkeys, about 40 chickens...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.03,0:26:29.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}50 sirloin steaks, two dozen of pork roast...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.39,0:26:32.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and 20 legs of lamb. Do you like lamb, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.52,0:26:34.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No. - You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.26,0:26:36.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, what's your favorite food, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.07,0:26:37.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}French fries and ketchup.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:40.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I think we can manage that too, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.95,0:26:42.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come along, now. Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.33,0:26:47.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Hallorann...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.28,0:26:51.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}how'd you know we call him Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.11,0:26:51.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.14,0:26:55.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doc. You called Danny "Doc" twice just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.36,0:26:57.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I did? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.50,0:26:58.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We call him Doc sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.82,0:27:00.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like in the Bugs Bunny cartoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.87,0:27:02.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But how did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.37,0:27:05.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I guess I probably heard you call him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.12,0:27:07.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, it's possible. But I honestly don't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.53,0:27:09.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}calling him that since we've been with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.98,0:27:12.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, anyway, he looks like a Doc, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.67,0:27:14.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's up, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.79,0:27:19.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, this is the storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.80,0:27:22.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In here, Mrs. Torrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.14,0:27:25.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is where we keep all the dried goods and the canned goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.89,0:27:28.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got canned fruits and vegetables...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.47,0:27:32.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}canned fish and meats, hot and cold cereals.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.48,0:27:35.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Post Toasties, Corn Flakes, Sugar Puffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.81,0:27:40.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rice Krispies, oatmeal, Wheatena and Cream of Wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.10,0:27:42.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You got a dozen jugs of black molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.71,0:27:45.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We got 60 boxes of dried milk...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.68,0:27:55.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How'd you like some ice cream, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.61,0:28:00.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sociables, finger rolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.61,0:28:02.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and 7 kinds of what have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.39,0:28:06.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, we've got dried peaches, dried apricots...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.19,0:28:08.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}dried raisins and dried prunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.95,0:28:10.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, Mrs. Torrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.57,0:28:13.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you got to keep regular if you want to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.70,0:28:18.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How're you getting on? - Just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.55,0:28:20.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dick, can we borrow Mrs. Torrance for a few minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.92,0:28:22.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're on our way through to the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.63,0:28:24.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I promise we won't keep her very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.40,0:28:27.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No problem, Mr. Ullman. I was just getting to the ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.87,0:28:30.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You like ice cream, Doc? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.48,0:28:31.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.76,0:28:32.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You folks don't mind
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.65,0:28:34.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if I give Danny some ice cream while we waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.96,0:28:37.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Not at all. - No, we don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.04,0:28:38.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Good. - Sound good to you, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.80,0:28:41.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah. - Okay, you behave yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.52,0:28:46.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What kind of ice cream do you like, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.59,0:28:47.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.66,0:28:50.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Chocolate it shall be. Come on, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.19,0:28:57.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's amazing, how much activities going on today.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.40,0:28:59.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes. Well, the guests and some of the staff left yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.73,0:29:01.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the last day's always hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.86,0:29:05.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody wants to be on their way as early as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.27,0:29:09.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}By 5 o'clock tonight, you'll never know anybody was ever here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.58,0:29:12.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Just like a ghost ship, huh? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.39,0:29:20.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know how I knew your name was Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.86,0:29:29.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know what I'm talking about, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.13,0:29:39.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can remember when I was a little boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.06,0:29:42.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}my grandmother and I could hold conversations
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.84,0:29:46.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}entirely without ever opening our mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.73,0:29:49.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She called it "Shining."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.67,0:29:53.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And for a long time I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.54,0:29:56.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it was just the two of us that had "the Shine" to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.70,0:30:00.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just like you probably thought you was the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.31,0:30:03.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But there are other folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.44,0:30:06.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}though mostly they don't know it, or don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.81,0:30:13.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How long have you been able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.45,0:30:21.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why don't you want to talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.09,0:30:28.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.71,0:30:32.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who says you ain't supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.75,0:30:37.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.05,0:30:41.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.26,0:30:47.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony's the little boy that lives in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.60,0:30:53.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is Tony the one that tells you things?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.96,0:30:55.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.96,0:30:59.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How does he tell you things?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.15,0:31:06.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's like I go to sleep, and he shows me things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.64,0:31:10.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But when I wake up, I can't remember everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.63,0:31:16.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does your mom and dad know about Tony?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.56,0:31:18.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.62,0:31:21.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do they know he tells you things?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.00,0:31:25.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony told me never to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.13,0:31:31.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Has Tony ever told you anything about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.69,0:31:34.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About the Overlook Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.56,0:31:38.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.94,0:31:42.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now think real hard, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.62,0:31:43.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.06,0:31:49.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe he showed me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.71,0:31:53.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Try to think of what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.37,0:31:59.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Hallorann, are you scared of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.46,0:32:04.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. Scared of nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.49,0:32:06.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.73,0:32:10.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you know, some places are like people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.38,0:32:14.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some shine and some don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.95,0:32:18.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess you could say the Overlook Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.00,0:32:21.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}has something about it that's like shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.77,0:32:26.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is there something bad here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.79,0:32:41.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, Doc, when something happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.42,0:32:44.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it can leave a trace of itself behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.92,0:32:47.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Say, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.64,0:32:50.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if someone burns toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.83,0:32:57.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe things that happen leave other kind of traces behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.64,0:33:01.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not things that anyone can notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.20,0:33:07.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But things that people who shine can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.16,0:33:11.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just like they can see things that haven't happened yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.80,0:33:17.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}sometimes they can see things that happened a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.40,0:33:22.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think a lot of things happened right here
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.46,0:33:26.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in this particular hotel over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.76,0:33:29.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And not all of them was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.45,0:33:34.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about room 237?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.49,0:33:40.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Room 237?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.96,0:33:44.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're scared of room 237, ain't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.77,0:33:48.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I ain't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.76,0:33:53.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Hallorann, what is in room 237?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.03,0:33:56.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.72,0:33:59.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There ain't nothing in room 237.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.21,0:34:03.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you ain't got no business going in there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.72,0:34:05.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So stay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.96,0:34:08.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You understand? Stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.54,0:34:13.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.00,0:35:49.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good morning, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.62,0:35:53.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.20,0:35:55.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.09,0:35:57.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's about 11:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.24,0:36:01.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eleven-thirty, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.34,0:36:04.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess we've been staying up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.04,0:36:06.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.89,0:36:10.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I made them just the way you like them, sunny-side up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.38,0:36:12.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.85,0:36:16.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's really pretty outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.87,0:36:19.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How about taking me for a walk after you finish your breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.72,0:36:24.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I suppose I ought to try to do some writing first.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.43,0:36:27.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any ideas yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.15,0:36:30.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lots of ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.07,0:36:32.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No good ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.06,0:36:35.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, something will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.89,0:36:39.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just a matter of settling into the habit of writing every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.53,0:36:42.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yep. That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.28,0:36:47.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's really nice up here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.01,0:36:49.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.01,0:36:51.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.61,0:36:55.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've never been this happy or comfortable anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.06,0:36:59.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's amazing how fast you get used to such a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.61,0:37:02.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I tell you, when we first came up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.64,0:37:04.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought it was kind of scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.20,0:37:07.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I fell in love with it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.48,0:37:11.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When I came up here for my interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.70,0:37:15.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it was as though I'd been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.70,0:37:18.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, we all have moments of déjà vu,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.55,0:37:20.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but this was ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.47,0:37:23.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was almost as though I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.73,0:37:26.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what was going to be around every corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.52,0:38:03.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The loser has to keep America clean. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.80,0:38:06.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- All right. - And you're going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.58,0:38:09.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I'm going to get you. You'd better run fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.67,0:38:15.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.12,0:38:18.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm coming in close. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.13,0:38:20.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Loser has to keep America clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.99,0:38:22.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.24,0:38:22.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Oh, no! - Keep America clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.37,0:38:23.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.64,0:38:24.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.29,0:38:26.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's take the rest of this walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.78,0:38:29.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Okay. - Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.22,0:38:31.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.15,0:38:35.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.28,0:38:37.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.68,0:38:55.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.19,0:39:53.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Woo, we made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.47,0:39:56.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Isn't it beautiful? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.52,0:40:19.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.04,0:40:21.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.17,0:40:26.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't think it was going to be this big. Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.98,0:40:27.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.09,0:40:32.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.33,0:40:40.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rutherford was serving a life sentence...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.11,0:40:42.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for his conviction in the 1968 shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.84,0:40:45.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the search continues in the mountains near Uray today
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.40,0:40:47.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for that missing Aspen woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.04,0:40:50.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Twenty-four-year-old Susan Robertson has been missing 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.53,0:40:53.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She disappeared while on a hunting trip with her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.45,0:40:54.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They have good weather right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.70,0:40:56.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they may have to call off the search...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.49,0:40:59.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if a predicted snowstorm moves in tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.17,0:41:00.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But it's so beautiful in Denver today,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.00,0:41:03.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it's hard to believe a snowstorm could be that close.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.70,0:41:06.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know. I want to go outside and lie in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.13,0:41:10.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yet to our north, to our west, it is snowing and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.23,0:41:14.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And it's moving right here towards Colorado as we talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.33,0:41:15.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.64,0:43:44.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.61,0:43:49.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.69,0:43:53.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.92,0:43:57.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get a lot written today?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.76,0:44:00.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.34,0:44:06.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, the weather forecast said it's going to snow tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.36,0:44:14.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you want me to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.12,0:44:18.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.27,0:44:20.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't be so grouchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.78,0:44:22.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.49,0:44:24.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}being grouchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.88,0:44:27.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just want to finish my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.13,0:44:33.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.72,0:44:36.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll come back later on with a couple of sandwiches for you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.62,0:44:38.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}maybe you'll let me read something then.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.23,0:44:43.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wendy,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.72,0:44:45.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}let me explain something to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.04,0:44:49.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whenever you come in here and interrupt me,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.34,0:44:51.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you're breaking my concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.21,0:44:52.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're distracting me,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.58,0:44:56.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and it will then take me time to get back to where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.49,0:44:57.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.52,0:45:00.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.39,0:45:02.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.64,0:45:05.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now we're going to make a new rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.59,0:45:06.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whenever I'm in here
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.30,0:45:08.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you hear me typing,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.25,0:45:12.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or whether you don't hear me typing,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.54,0:45:14.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or whatever the fuck you hear me doing in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.24,0:45:16.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when I'm in here, that means I am working,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.83,0:45:18.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that means don't come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.34,0:45:21.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, do you think you can handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.25,0:45:25.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.19,0:45:27.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.40,0:45:31.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why don't you start right now and get the fuck out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.41,0:45:36.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.20,0:46:04.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.69,0:46:08.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.44,0:46:12.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you've got more.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.48,0:46:15.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.94,0:46:22.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't have!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.03,0:46:23.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No fair anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.51,0:46:55.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.86,0:47:22.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.51,0:47:32.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.97,0:48:06.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is KDK 12 calling KDK 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.98,0:48:12.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}KDK 12 to KDK 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.98,0:48:15.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is KDK 1. We're receiving you. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.41,0:48:19.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, this is Wendy Torrance at the Overlook Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.09,0:48:22.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, how are you folks getting on up there? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.11,0:48:24.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.69,0:48:27.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But our telephones don't seem to be doing too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.40,0:48:30.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are the lines down, by any chance? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.05,0:48:34.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, quite a few of them are down due to the storm. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.10,0:48:38.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any chance of them being repaired soon? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.49,0:48:39.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I wouldn't like to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.93,0:48:43.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Most winters they stay that way until spring. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.86,0:48:47.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Boy, this storm is really something, isn't it? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.75,0:48:50.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes. It's one of the worst we've had for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.12,0:48:54.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is there anything else we can do for you, Mrs. Torrance? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.88,0:48:57.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I suppose not. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.64,0:49:00.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you folks have any problems up there, just give us a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.09,0:49:02.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And, Mrs. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.61,0:49:03.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think it might be a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.94,0:49:07.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if you leave your radio on all the time now. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.69,0:49:09.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. We'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.42,0:49:11.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was real nice talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.66,0:49:13.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bye. Over and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.25,0:49:51.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.67,0:49:58.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come and play with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.99,0:50:06.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come and play with us, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.68,0:50:10.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.27,0:50:13.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.06,0:50:16.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.52,0:50:49.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tony,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.00,0:50:52.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.56,0:51:01.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Remember what Mr. Hallorann said.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.77,0:51:07.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just like pictures in a book, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.91,0:51:09.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It isn't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.50,0:51:20.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.46,0:51:23.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please let me give you some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.48,0:51:25.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wouldn't think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.71,0:51:27.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, how can I repay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.01,0:51:29.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.49,0:51:32.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I'm going to have some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.83,0:51:34.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.11,0:51:37.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.33,0:51:38.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Great. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.18,0:51:51.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ooh, these marvellous doughnuts. Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.34,0:51:55.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Coffee will be ready in a few minutes. - Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.76,0:51:58.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.65,0:52:02.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can I go up to my room and get my fire-engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.37,0:52:06.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not right now. Daddy's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.15,0:52:09.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I won't make any noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.72,0:52:13.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.69,0:52:15.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He only went to bed a few hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.78,0:52:17.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can't you wait till later?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.69,0:52:20.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I won't make a sound. I promise I'll tiptoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.69,0:52:25.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.52,0:52:27.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But really don't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.17,0:52:29.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I won't, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.54,0:52:32.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Make sure you come right back,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.23,0:52:34.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because I'm going to make lunch soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.22,0:52:37.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Okay? - Okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.24,0:53:30.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can I go to my room and get my fire-engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.10,0:53:36.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come here for a minute first.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.52,0:54:14.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's it going, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.56,0:54:17.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.71,0:54:21.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Having a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.63,0:54:24.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.05,0:54:28.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.55,0:54:33.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.38,0:54:35.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.39,0:54:43.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.24,0:54:44.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.37,0:54:47.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you feel bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.92,0:54:51.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.17,0:54:55.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just a little bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.00,0:54:59.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then why don't you go to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.17,0:55:05.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.20,0:55:08.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got too much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.82,0:55:13.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.95,0:55:16.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.62,0:55:20.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you like this hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.45,0:55:25.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.05,0:55:27.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.44,0:55:30.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.90,0:55:33.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.64,0:55:37.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.78,0:55:41.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.19,0:55:47.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.56,0:55:54.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wish we could stay here forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.17,0:55:56.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.45,0:55:58.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.36,0:56:02.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.33,0:56:05.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.63,0:56:09.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You would never hurt Mommy or me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.36,0:56:16.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.85,0:56:23.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did your mother ever say that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.14,0:56:26.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That I would hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.61,0:56:28.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.26,0:56:32.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.31,0:56:34.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.79,0:56:41.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love you, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.87,0:56:47.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love you more than anything else in the whole world,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.20,0:56:51.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I would never do anything to hurt you,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.45,0:56:53.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}never.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.57,0:56:56.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.00,0:56:58.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.63,0:57:00.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.18,0:57:05.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.17,0:57:42.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.46,0:58:02.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.58,0:58:29.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mom, are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.21,0:58:59.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.03,0:59:35.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.36,0:59:40.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack? Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.25,0:59:44.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.60,0:59:50.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.88,0:59:51.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.05,0:59:53.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.24,0:59:55.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.43,1:00:06.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had the most terrible nightmare I ever had.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.57,1:00:12.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It was the most horrible dream. - It's okay, it's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.78,1:00:13.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.64,1:00:19.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I dreamed that I...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.39,1:00:22.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that I killed you and Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.49,1:00:27.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I didn't just kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.16,1:00:31.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I cut you up into little pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.38,1:00:35.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.62,1:00:38.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I must be losing my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.49,1:00:43.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everything's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.25,1:00:48.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on. Let's get up off the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.84,1:00:58.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay. There. Now sit up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.75,1:01:00.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.19,1:01:02.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.70,1:01:08.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.10,1:01:10.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everything's okay!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.27,1:01:13.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just go play in your room for a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.76,1:01:16.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your dad's just got a headache.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.09,1:01:20.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny, mind what I say. Go play in your room.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.23,1:01:25.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Honey, let me just go get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.37,1:01:27.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.20,1:01:29.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.79,1:01:31.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why don't you mind me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.65,1:01:35.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.46,1:01:39.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.56,1:01:43.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny, what happened to your neck?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.64,1:01:47.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny, what happened to your neck?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.88,1:02:18.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You did this to him...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.31,1:02:20.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.35,1:02:24.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.84,1:02:26.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You did this to him!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.93,1:02:27.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.73,1:02:30.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.68,1:02:32.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.38,1:03:17.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.20,1:04:05.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God! I'd give anything for a drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.56,1:04:11.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd give my goddamn soul...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.22,1:04:13.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for just a glass of beer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.48,1:04:30.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.56,1:04:36.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A little slow tonight, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.86,1:04:43.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, it is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.21,1:04:47.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What will it be?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.27,1:04:52.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm awfully glad you asked me that, Lloyd...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.63,1:04:55.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because I just happen to have two twenties
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.92,1:04:58.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and two tens right here in my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.22,1:05:02.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was afraid they were going to be there until next April.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.02,1:05:04.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So here's what:
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.27,1:05:07.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You slip me a bottle of bourbon...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.75,1:05:09.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A little glass and some ice.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.73,1:05:12.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can do that, can't you, Lloyd?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.18,1:05:15.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not too busy, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.26,1:05:18.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, sir. I'm not busy at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.06,1:05:20.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good man.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.90,1:05:23.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You set them up and I'll knock them back, Lloyd,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.23,1:05:24.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}one by one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.40,1:05:29.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}White man's burden, Lloyd, my man.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.57,1:05:31.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}White man's burden.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.86,1:05:38.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Say, Lloyd...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.83,1:05:41.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it seems I'm temporarily light.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.17,1:05:44.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's my credit in this joint, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.89,1:05:46.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your credit's fine, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.06,1:05:49.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's swell.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.86,1:05:51.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I like you, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.65,1:05:53.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I always liked you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.62,1:05:55.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were always the best of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.07,1:06:01.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Best goddamned bartender from Timbuktu to Portland, Maine.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.88,1:06:04.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or Portland, Oregon, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.44,1:06:05.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you for saying so.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.42,1:06:12.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here's to five miserable months on the wagon
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.24,1:06:16.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and all the irreparable harm that it's caused me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.48,1:06:37.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How are things going, Mr. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.40,1:06:41.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Things could be better, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.29,1:06:45.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Things could be a whole lot better.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.10,1:06:48.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.58,1:06:50.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.31,1:06:53.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.81,1:07:01.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just a little problem with the old sperm bank upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.11,1:07:04.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing I can't handle, though, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.78,1:07:05.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.92,1:07:07.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Women.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.02,1:07:09.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can't live with them
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.80,1:07:11.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}can't live without them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.93,1:07:16.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Words of wisdom, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.54,1:07:19.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Words of wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.32,1:07:33.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never laid a hand on him, goddamn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.80,1:07:35.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.34,1:07:42.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wouldn't touch one hair on his goddamn little head.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.61,1:07:46.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love the little son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.38,1:07:50.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd do anything for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.33,1:07:53.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Any fucking thing for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.47,1:08:00.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.73,1:08:03.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As long as I live...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.90,1:08:06.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}she'll never let me forget what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.76,1:08:19.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I did hurt him once, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.03,1:08:21.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.45,1:08:24.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Completely unintentional.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.28,1:08:28.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It could have happened to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.28,1:08:33.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And it was three goddamn years ago!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.92,1:08:36.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The little fucker had thrown all my papers all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.69,1:08:38.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All I tried to do was pull him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.12,1:08:46.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A momentary loss of muscular coordination.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.16,1:08:48.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.84,1:08:52.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A few extra foot-pounds of energy...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.49,1:08:54.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}per second, per second.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.09,1:09:01.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.89,1:09:11.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.59,1:09:13.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank God you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.42,1:09:16.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.72,1:09:18.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's someone else in the hotel with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.12,1:09:21.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a crazy woman in one of the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.99,1:09:23.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She tried to strangle Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.91,1:09:29.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you out of your fucking mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.71,1:09:30.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.32,1:09:32.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's the truth! Really.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.96,1:09:35.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I swear it. Danny told me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.87,1:09:37.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He went up into one of the bedrooms.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.95,1:09:41.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The door was open, and he saw this crazy woman in the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.67,1:09:43.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She tried to strangle him!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.63,1:09:49.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which room was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.26,1:09:59.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From Channel 10 in Miami...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.45,1:10:01.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this is Newswatch
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.04,1:10:03.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with Glenn Rinker, Ann Bishop,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.20,1:10:05.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the award-winning Newswatch team.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.72,1:10:09.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good evening. I'm Glenn Rinker, Newswatch Ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.36,1:10:12.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}While Miami continues to swelter in a record winter heatwave
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.64,1:10:15.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}bringing temperatures to the mid and upper nineties,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.02,1:10:18.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the Central and Rocky Mountain States are buried in snow.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.37,1:10:19.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In Colorado,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.30,1:10:22.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}10 inches of snow has fallen in just a few hours tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.54,1:10:25.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Travel in the Rockies is almost impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.04,1:10:28.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Airports are shut down, stranding thousands of passengers.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.16,1:10:30.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Highways are blocked by snowdrifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.32,1:10:32.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Railroad tracks are frozen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.34,1:10:34.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Officials in Colorado tell Newswatch...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.46,1:10:38.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at least three have been killed by exposure to freezing winds.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.26,1:10:40.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The governor of Colorado is expected tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.62,1:10:42.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to declare a weather emergency.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.69,1:10:44.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The National Guard might be called out...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.41,1:10:46.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to clear streets and roads.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.18,1:10:48.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Weather forecasters predict more snow...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.52,1:10:50.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and heavy winds tonight and tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.71,1:10:53.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with temperatures dropping well below zero.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.48,1:10:56.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Back here in south Florida, we've got the opposite problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.80,1:10:59.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The heat and humidity are supposed to climb.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.34,1:11:01.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Local beaches should be jammed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.49,1:11:03.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Our weather expert, Walter Cronice...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.72,1:11:06.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}will have the local forecast later on Newswatch.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.10,1:11:42.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.32,1:16:43.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're sorry. Your call cannot be completed as dialed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.41,1:16:45.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you need assistance, please call the operator.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.23,1:17:03.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.93,1:17:05.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.01,1:17:06.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.99,1:17:13.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you find anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.07,1:17:16.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.45,1:17:19.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't see one goddamn thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.30,1:17:26.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You went into the room Danny said? To 237?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.87,1:17:28.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.89,1:17:30.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you didn't see anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.06,1:17:32.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.15,1:17:34.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.60,1:17:36.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's still asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.86,1:17:37.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.83,1:17:46.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure he'll be himself again in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.45,1:17:53.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you sure it was the right room?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.13,1:17:57.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I mean, maybe Danny made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.48,1:17:59.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He must have gone in that room.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.93,1:18:02.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The door was open, the lights were on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.23,1:18:07.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.13,1:18:14.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about those bruises on his neck?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.21,1:18:19.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Somebody did that to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.84,1:18:28.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.85,1:18:32.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he did it to himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.52,1:18:40.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.36,1:18:42.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.96,1:18:46.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.68,1:18:52.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}once you rule out his version of what happened...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.59,1:18:54.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}there is no other explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.64,1:18:56.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.29,1:19:02.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It wouldn't be that different from the episode...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.39,1:19:05.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that he had before we came up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.08,1:19:06.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.67,1:19:13.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.22,1:19:17.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever the explanation is...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.48,1:19:19.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.62,1:19:22.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think we...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.33,1:19:25.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}have to get Danny out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.79,1:19:32.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get him out of here?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.27,1:19:34.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.86,1:19:40.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You mean just leave the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.55,1:19:43.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.80,1:19:54.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is so fucking typical of you to create a problem like this
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.72,1:19:57.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when I finally have a chance to accomplish something!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.61,1:19:59.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When I'm really into my work!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.52,1:20:01.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could really write my own ticket
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.85,1:20:04.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if I went back to Boulder now, couldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.67,1:20:08.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shoveling out driveways, work in a car wash.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.37,1:20:10.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Any of that appeal to you? - Jack...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.65,1:20:14.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wendy, I have let you fuck up my life so far,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.61,1:20:17.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I am not going to let you fuck this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.23,1:21:38.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good evening. Forest Service.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.19,1:21:40.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, my name is Dick Hallorann.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.83,1:21:43.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm the head chef up at the Overlook Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.49,1:21:45.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good evening, Mr. Hallorann. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.74,1:21:49.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sir, I've been trying to make an urgent phone call up there,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.65,1:21:52.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the operator said that the phone lines are down.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.04,1:21:55.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I'm afraid a lot of lines around here are down
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.11,1:21:56.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}due to the storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.74,1:21:59.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, look sir, I hate to put you through any trouble,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.80,1:22:03.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but there's a family up there all by themselves with a young kid,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.22,1:22:05.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and with this storm and everything...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.07,1:22:08.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd sure appreciate it if you'd give them a call on your radio
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.14,1:22:10.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just to see if everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.60,1:22:12.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll be glad to do that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.23,1:22:15.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why don't you call me back in about 20 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.23,1:22:17.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you very much. I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.35,1:22:18.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.20,1:22:41.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good evening, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.25,1:22:42.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.40,1:23:08.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.94,1:23:11.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've been away, but now I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.10,1:23:12.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good evening, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.48,1:23:14.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.03,1:23:17.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's good to be back, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.14,1:23:19.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What'll it be, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.69,1:23:23.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hair of the dog that bit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.25,1:23:26.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bourbon on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.69,1:23:28.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That'll do her.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.63,1:23:43.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No charge to you, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.39,1:23:47.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No charge?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.00,1:23:49.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your money's no good here.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.49,1:23:57.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Orders from the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.58,1:24:02.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Orders from the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.24,1:24:08.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Drink up, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.44,1:24:14.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm the kind of man likes to know who's buying their drinks, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.48,1:24:20.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not a matter that concerns you, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.44,1:24:22.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}At least, not at this point.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.16,1:24:29.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anything you say, Lloyd.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.10,1:24:31.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.05,1:24:47.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, dear! Oh, dear! I'm so sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.84,1:24:50.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, dear. Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.36,1:24:52.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've made an awful mess of your jacket, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.74,1:24:57.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, that's all right. I've got plenty of jackets.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.81,1:25:00.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm afraid it's advocaat, sir. It tends to stain.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.04,1:25:02.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Advocaat, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.24,1:25:04.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir. Look, I think the best thing
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.28,1:25:06.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is to come along to the gentlemen's room, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.07,1:25:09.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and we'll get some water to it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.49,1:25:13.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Looks as though you might have got a spot of it on yourself there,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.57,1:25:15.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jeevesy old boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.33,1:25:16.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That doesn't matter, sir. You...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.41,1:25:18.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're the important one.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.60,1:25:20.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Awfully nice of you to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.38,1:25:24.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course, I intended to change my jacket this evening
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.39,1:25:27.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}before the fish and goose soiree.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.21,1:25:29.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very wise, sir. Very wise.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.19,1:25:33.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here. I'll just hold this for you there, Jeevesy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.99,1:25:35.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you, sir. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.57,1:25:40.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now let's see if we can improve this with a little water, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.71,1:25:41.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right. I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.97,1:25:45.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}set my bourbon and advocaat down right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.85,1:25:48.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Won't keep you a moment, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.36,1:25:49.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.74,1:25:54.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do they call you around here, Jeevesy?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.81,1:25:57.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grady, sir. Delbert Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.03,1:26:03.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grady?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.09,1:26:04.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.53,1:26:07.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Delbert Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.07,1:26:08.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.37,1:26:18.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Grady...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.50,1:26:21.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Haven't I seen you somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.83,1:26:24.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why, no, sir. I don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.63,1:26:33.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's coming off now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.33,1:26:39.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Grady,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.46,1:26:43.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}weren't you once the caretaker here?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.10,1:26:46.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why, no, sir. I don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.92,1:26:53.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You a married man, are you, Mr. Grady?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.43,1:26:54.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.59,1:26:57.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have a wife and two daughters, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.94,1:27:00.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.02,1:27:03.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}where are they now?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.47,1:27:04.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're somewhere around.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.16,1:27:07.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not quite sure at the moment, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.60,1:27:16.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Grady,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.25,1:27:20.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you were the caretaker here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.05,1:27:23.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.55,1:27:28.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saw your picture in the newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.02,1:27:30.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.22,1:27:34.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}chopped your wife and daughters up into little bits.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.35,1:27:36.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.19,1:27:39.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you blew your brains out.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.18,1:27:50.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's strange, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.83,1:27:54.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't have any recollection of that at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.36,1:27:59.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Grady,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.70,1:28:03.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you were the caretaker here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.74,1:28:14.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry to differ with you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.42,1:28:17.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.86,1:28:20.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}are the caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.04,1:28:25.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've always been the caretaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.87,1:28:30.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I should know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.91,1:28:34.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've always been here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.80,1:28:54.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you know, Mr. Torrance,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.17,1:28:56.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that your son...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.47,1:29:02.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is attempting to bring an outside party into this situation?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.12,1:29:06.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.45,1:29:11.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.10,1:29:14.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.43,1:29:18.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.86,1:29:22.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A nigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.56,1:29:27.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A nigger?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.72,1:29:33.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A nigger cook.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.89,1:29:41.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.47,1:29:48.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your son has a very great talent.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.43,1:29:52.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think you are aware how great it is,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.62,1:29:56.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but he is attempting to use that very talent
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.08,1:29:58.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}against your will.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.63,1:30:14.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He is a very willful boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.20,1:30:19.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Indeed he is, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.80,1:30:22.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A very willful boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.87,1:30:26.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A rather naughty boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.11,1:30:29.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if I may be so bold, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.70,1:30:38.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's his mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.54,1:30:43.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She interferes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.25,1:30:51.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perhaps they need a good talking-to.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.58,1:30:56.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you don't mind my saying so.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.20,1:31:00.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perhaps a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.23,1:31:05.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My girls, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.55,1:31:09.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they didn't care for the Overlook at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.18,1:31:14.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One of them actually stole a pack of matches
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.54,1:31:16.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and tried to burn it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.12,1:31:21.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I corrected them, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.22,1:31:27.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when my wife tried to prevent me from doing my duty,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.52,1:31:31.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I corrected her.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.05,1:31:47.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have the Snowcat.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.69,1:31:53.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If the weather breaks,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.42,1:31:57.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we might just be able to get down the mountain in that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.26,1:32:02.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could call the forest rangers first
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.32,1:32:06.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then tell them that we're coming
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.29,1:32:12.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so that they could start searching for us, in case we didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.44,1:32:18.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if Jack won't come with us,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.12,1:32:24.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we'll just have to tell him that we're going by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.00,1:32:26.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.37,1:32:29.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.81,1:32:32.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.67,1:32:36.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Redrum. Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.01,1:32:38.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Danny? - Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.86,1:32:42.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Redrum. Redrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.66,1:32:44.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Redrum. - Danny, what's the matter, hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.92,1:32:46.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Redrum!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.26,1:32:48.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you having a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.95,1:32:51.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.20,1:32:55.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.29,1:33:05.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny's not here, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.22,1:33:11.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, hon.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.63,1:33:14.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.16,1:33:17.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You just had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.77,1:33:20.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.95,1:33:28.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny can't wake up, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.89,1:33:37.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.32,1:33:39.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.15,1:33:42.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.73,1:33:44.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.72,1:33:46.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.20,1:33:54.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny's gone away, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.14,1:33:58.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.29,1:34:06.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.42,1:34:10.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.73,1:34:12.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you receiving me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.95,1:34:18.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.43,1:34:22.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.46,1:34:23.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.62,1:34:31.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.64,1:34:34.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.41,1:34:36.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you receiving me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.99,1:34:41.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.03,1:34:44.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.25,1:34:46.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.28,1:34:53.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is KDK 1 calling KDK 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.55,1:34:58.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}KDK 1 calling KDK 12. Are you receiv-
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.74,1:35:14.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good evening. Forest service.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.67,1:35:17.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello. This is Dick Hallorann again.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.18,1:35:20.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I called a while ago about the folks at the Overlook Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.43,1:35:21.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.49,1:35:23.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We tried to contact them several times by radio
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.72,1:35:25.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.48,1:35:27.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe they got their radio turned off
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.13,1:35:29.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or they are in a place where they can't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.31,1:35:32.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you'd like, I'd be glad to try again later on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.88,1:35:34.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's very nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.05,1:35:36.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.94,1:35:38.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.85,1:35:51.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.09,1:36:28.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pardon me, miss. What time will we get to Denver?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.35,1:36:30.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're due to arrive at 8:20, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.70,1:36:32.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.89,1:37:25.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.19,1:37:37.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Durkin's Garage.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.47,1:37:38.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can I speak to Larry?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.73,1:37:39.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Speaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.96,1:37:42.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hi, Larry. This is Dick. Dick Hallorann.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.69,1:37:44.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dick! How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.60,1:37:46.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How's the weather down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.17,1:37:47.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not in Florida, Larry.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.25,1:37:49.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm calling from Stapleton Airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.68,1:37:51.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell are you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.71,1:37:55.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just got in from Miami. I got to get to the Overlook today.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.36,1:37:57.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the weather like there?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.46,1:38:00.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The snowplows are keeping things moving in town...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.74,1:38:02.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but the mountain roads are blocked.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.25,1:38:06.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then I'm going to need a Snowcat to get up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.17,1:38:07.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you fix me up with one?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.20,1:38:10.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's the big deal about getting there today...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.45,1:38:12.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}especially in this kind of weather?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.86,1:38:14.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Larry, just between you and me,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.64,1:38:17.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we got a very serious problem with the people
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.10,1:38:18.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who are taking care of the place.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.07,1:38:22.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They turned out to be completely unreliable assholes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.01,1:38:25.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ullman phoned me last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.08,1:38:26.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I'm supposed to go up there
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.14,1:38:28.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and find out if they have to be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.95,1:38:31.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How long will it take you to get up here?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.24,1:38:34.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}About five hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.14,1:38:36.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm going to rent a car here at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.92,1:38:38.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, Dick, I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.06,1:38:41.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks a lot, Larry. I really appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.92,1:38:44.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all right. Drive carefully.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.23,1:38:51.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, good morning to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.03,1:38:53.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're with Hal and Charlie on Radio 63, KHOW, Denver.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.85,1:38:56.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Charlie, we have what you call your bad day out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.65,1:38:57.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What you call your heavy snow,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.61,1:39:00.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}snowing hard throughout the Denver metro area.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.27,1:39:01.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Many mountain passes...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.72,1:39:04.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wolf Creek and Red Mountain passes are already closed...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.89,1:39:08.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the chain law is in effect right now at the Eisenhower Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.49,1:39:09.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess as we've just heard from the news forecast,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.88,1:39:13.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}only a few flights are landing at Stapleton Airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.54,1:39:15.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, with these early storms like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.34,1:39:18.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess the entire airport will probably be closed within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.69,1:39:19.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, they're just not prepared.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.63,1:39:21.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The storm will continue through the day
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.54,1:39:22.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the National Weather Service
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.88,1:39:25.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}has declared a stockman's and traveler's advisory
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.42,1:39:28.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for all areas outlying the Denver metro region.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.39,1:39:29.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get the cows in the barn.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.68,1:39:31.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you go.  Many businesses...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.07,1:39:52.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.26,1:39:59.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen to me for a minute, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.66,1:40:06.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just going to go and talk to Daddy for a few minutes...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.38,1:40:09.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.53,1:40:12.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you to just stay here...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.14,1:40:15.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and watch your cartoons, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.76,1:40:20.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay, hon?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.54,1:40:25.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, Mrs. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.16,1:40:36.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.49,1:40:40.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll- I'll be back in just about five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.20,1:40:44.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm going to lock the door behind me.
