Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.32,1:42:43.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.00,1:43:05.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.91,1:43:41.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.83,1:44:12.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.54,1:44:15.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.05,1:44:20.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.71,1:44:32.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What are you doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.60,1:44:39.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.56,1:44:41.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}wanted...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.92,1:44:43.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.93,1:44:47.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.80,1:44:49.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.20,1:45:00.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.12,1:45:08.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.07,1:45:11.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't really remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.12,1:45:14.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.99,1:45:19.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No... I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.44,1:45:27.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe it was about Danny?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.08,1:45:32.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe it was about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.31,1:45:39.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think we should discuss Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.35,1:45:41.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.38,1:45:44.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.72,1:45:48.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we should discuss what should be done with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.24,1:45:55.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What should be done with him?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.63,1:46:02.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.05,1:46:05.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.24,1:46:08.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think you have some very definite ideas...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.05,1:46:10.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about what should be done with Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.03,1:46:12.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I'd like to know what they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.43,1:46:16.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.59,1:46:20.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think maybe he should be taken to a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.17,1:46:24.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You think "maybe" he should be taken to a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.57,1:46:25.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.12,1:46:29.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When do you think "maybe" he should be taken to a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.62,1:46:32.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As soon as possible?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.71,1:46:34.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"As soon as possible?"
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.29,1:46:36.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.59,1:46:38.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.47,1:46:43.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You believe his health might be at stake.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.25,1:46:46.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.33,1:46:50.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you are concerned about him.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.10,1:46:52.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.45,1:46:55.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And are you concerned about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.61,1:46:57.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.91,1:46:59.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course you are!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.63,1:47:03.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you ever thought about my responsibilities?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.43,1:47:05.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Jack, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.37,1:47:08.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you ever had a single moment's
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.20,1:47:10.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}thought about my responsibilities?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.43,1:47:13.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you ever thought for a single solitary moment
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.00,1:47:15.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about my responsibilities to my employers?!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.07,1:47:17.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Has it ever occurred to you
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.11,1:47:21.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that I have agreed to look after the hotel until May 1st?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.88,1:47:24.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does it matter to you at all
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.18,1:47:27.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that the owners have placed their complete confidence and trust in me
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.28,1:47:29.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and that I have signed a letter of agreement.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.40,1:47:30.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A contract
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.78,1:47:33.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in which I've accepted that responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.72,1:47:36.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you have the slightest idea
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.08,1:47:38.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what a moral and ethical principal is? Do you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.65,1:47:42.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Has it ever occurred to you what would happen to my future
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.88,1:47:45.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if I fail to live up to my responsibilities?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.52,1:47:48.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Has it ever occurred to you? Has it?!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.04,1:47:49.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.37,1:47:51.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.93,1:47:54.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just want to go back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.03,1:47:56.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.90,1:48:01.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm very confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.05,1:48:05.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I just need a chance to think things over.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.82,1:48:10.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've had your whole fucking life to think things over!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.94,1:48:13.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What good's a few minutes more going to do you now?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.56,1:48:16.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.39,1:48:17.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.56,1:48:19.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.99,1:48:21.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.27,1:48:22.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.32,1:48:23.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Wendy. - Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.73,1:48:25.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.04,1:48:26.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Light of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.20,1:48:28.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.64,1:48:30.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't let me finish my sentence.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.80,1:48:33.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I said, "I'm not going to hurt you. "
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.16,1:48:35.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm just going to bash your brains in.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.40,1:48:38.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm going to bash them right the fuck in.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.29,1:48:41.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.27,1:48:43.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.69,1:48:45.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not going to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.21,1:48:47.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.77,1:48:49.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.87,1:48:51.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.49,1:48:54.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop swinging the bat.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.02,1:48:55.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.16,1:48:57.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Put that bat down, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.62,1:48:59.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.41,1:49:00.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.66,1:49:01.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give me the bat.
