Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.39,1:55:03.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:05.35,1:55:07.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's Grady, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.35,1:55:10.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Delbert Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.10,1:55:13.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grady?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.40,1:55:20.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.62,1:55:26.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grady, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.92,1:55:35.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.46,1:55:41.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr. Torrance...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.14,1:55:47.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I see you can hardly have taken care of the...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:48.06,1:55:51.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}business we discussed.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.90,1:56:00.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No need to rub it in, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.65,1:56:05.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll deal with that situation as soon as I get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.62,1:56:09.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will you indeed, Mr. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.87,1:56:11.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.83,1:56:14.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have my doubts.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.08,1:56:20.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I, and others, have come to believe...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.59,1:56:23.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that your heart is not in this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.30,1:56:26.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That you haven't the belly for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.04,1:56:36.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just give me one more chance to prove it, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.11,1:56:39.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.53,1:56:45.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your wife appears to be stronger than we imagined, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.95,1:56:47.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Somewhat more...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.66,1:56:49.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}resourceful.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:49.95,1:56:52.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She seems to have got the better of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.08,1:56:58.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For the moment, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.38,1:57:01.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.38,1:57:07.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I fear you will have to deal with this matter...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.84,1:57:11.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the harshest possible way, Mr. Torrance.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.10,1:57:13.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I fear...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.93,1:57:16.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that is the only thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.98,1:57:25.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's nothing I look forward to with greater pleasure, Mr. Grady.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.57,1:57:29.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You give your word on that, do you, Mr. Torrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.78,1:57:33.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I give you my word.
